target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/tiny-musical.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/tinymusical.jpg" alt="Tiny Musical / Akira Kosemura" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/tiny-musical.php">Tiny Musical<br />Akira Kosemura</a></h4><p>音色や構成がとてもかっこいい作品。インパクトがある音がモチベーションを上げてくれます。また、美しいピアノも本作の魅力です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B001E472PM?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B001E472PM" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Tiny Musical-Akira Kosemura']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Ftiny-musical%252Fid287562252%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Tiny Musical-Akira Kosemura']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/navigators-yard.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/nagivatorsyard.jpg" alt="Navigators Yard / Dakota Suite" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/navigators-yard.php">Navigators Yard<br />Dakota Suite</a></h4><p>音に空白が多く、シンプルでシリアル感を感じさせる作品です。美しく緊迫感のあるアコースティックサウンドは何度でも聴きたくなります。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00002DFKC?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00002DFKC" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Navigators Yard-Dakota Suite']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fnavigators-yard%252Fid262189080%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Navigators Yard-Dakota Suite']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/moanin.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/moanin.jpg" alt="Moanin' / The Jazz Messengers" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/moanin.php">Moanin'<br />The Jazz Messengers</a></h4><p>大人の余裕を感じさせる作品です。軽快な演奏なのにシリアスさを感じさせるあたりはさすがとしか言いようがありません。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00000I8UF?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00000I8UF" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Moanin'-The Jazz Messengers']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fmoanin-the-rudy-van-gelder%252Fid74168137%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Moanin'-The Jazz Messengers']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/open-sesame.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/freddieopen.jpg" alt="Open Sesame / Freddie Hubbard" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/open-sesame.php">Open Sesame<br />Freddie Hubbard</a></h4><p>バップならではの目まぐるしさがあり、聴けば聴くほどやる気が出てくるような躍動感と素晴らしい演奏が魅力の1枚です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00005UOKP?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00005UOKP" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Open Sesame-Freddie Hubbard']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fopen-sesame-the-rudy-van-gelder%252Fid75036388%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Open Sesame-Freddie Hubbard']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/as-the-earth-dances.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/astheearth.jpg" alt="As the Earth Dances / Nyolfen" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/as-the-earth-dances.php">As the Earth Dances<br />Nyolfen</a></h4><p>都会の音楽を感じさせるかっこいい音楽です。テクノorエレクトロニカといった内容で気合いを入れる時に聴きたい音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003DMTHZG?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003DMTHZG" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'As the Earth Dances-Nyolfen']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fas-the-earth-dances%252Fid378985146%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'As the Earth Dances-Nyolfen']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/with-you.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/withyou.jpg" alt="With You / Natalie Walker" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/with-you.php">With You<br />Natalie Walker</a></h4><p>エレクトロニカのような音色と演奏と分離して聴こえてしまうような、独特なヴォーカルが不思議と一体感と緊張感を生み出しています。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B001ASIS5U?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B001ASIS5U" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'With You-Natalie Walker']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fwith-you%252Fid282489909%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'With You-Natalie Walker']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/love-part-2.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/buildinpark.jpg" alt="Love Part 2 / Build An Ark" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/love-part-2.php">Love Part 2<br />Build An Ark</a></h4><p>頭がとろけてしまうような音色やジャズがベースとなった演奏が面白い雰囲気を作り出しています。民族楽器なども使われていて不思議とずっと聴いていたくなります。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003COBR1W?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003COBR1W" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Love Part 2-Build An Ark']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Flove-part-2%252Fid378147176%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Love Part 2-Build An Ark']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

